# Summary
This documentation explains Apple's iOS 14 IDFA changes requiring user opt-in for tracking, noting that Amplitude's iOS SDK uses IDFV by default as device identifier, and detailing how these changes affect user tracking, attribution events, and outbound integrations for both anonymous and logged-in users.

